author: jkaputin
msg: Removed the version number from interfaces and classes
beginning 'WSDL' because it seems unnecessary as the
package names already contain 'wsdl20', and any back
level support for wsdl 1.1 will probably use the JWSDL
api which has different names, and future versions of
WSDL are likely to be too far off to worry about yet.
